HOME.ENCRYPTED_PROTECTED_BY: Ekitibwa, okwefuga, n'okulwanyisa eby'enfuna obutalina ku by'okulonda ky'ekibanja
HOME.WITHOUT_TRACE_DESCRIPTION: Tukirindaamu ku buno obutafuna kubisinga eby'enfuna. Byonna birina okwekebejebwa ku mukutu. Tetukimanyi ku IP yawe, kye wogedde, oba kiki ky'oguddewo - era ekikulu, eby'okulonda.
HOME.PRIVACY_PROTECTED_DESCRIPTION: Ono ye asinga okutegeera ekiteeso ku nkola ya tekinologiya gyo ne bye y'osanga. Bw'otandika ekiteeso, osobola okuteekamu ekiteeso omukutu osinga okuggyeko. Era ky'osobola okukozesa ekiseera ky'enkola. Noolwekyo, ekiteeso kityo kimala okuva mu nnaku 14.
HOME.END_TO_END_ENCRYPTED_DESCRIPTION: Eby'olugambo n'ebikozesebwa byonna byakaddibwako ku mukutu, nga totulina kitukiririza mu link n'ebikozesebwa. Buli link erina ID ey'enjawulo ya 36 ey'ekikozesebwa okubala okutegeeza Ekiteeso n'ebikozesebwa ebyakaddibwako na AES-256.
HOME.SHARE_ENCRYPTED_BY: Ekitibwa, okwefuga, n'okulwanyisa eby'enfuna obutalina ku by'okulonda ky'ekibanja
HOME.SHARE_TEXTAREA_PLACEHOLDER: Yandikamu ekiteeso ky'ekibanja, ekiteeso, oba eby'enfuna *
